dc_title_s: Zaire city map 1:12,500. Bukavu. Series Z901
dc_description_s: North Decimal Degree -2.451111. South Decimal Degree -2.532500. East Decimal Degree 28.913889. West Decimal Degree 28.824167. Alternate title: Bukavu.
